From 3d1611fee726e524106ff746e133c490ba7b9bd7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alessio Ferri <alessio.ferri@mythread.it>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:58:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 6/9] b43: AC-PHY init, channel tuning, RF sequencer, and TX
 power

Wire the complete AC-PHY ops for BCM4352/BCM4360 (radio 2069 rev 4):
op_init, op_software_rfkill, set_channel (full sequence), TX power
control, RX gain init, ADC/AFE reset, idle-TSSI, farrow sample-rate.

New files: rxiqcal_phy_ac.c/h (skeleton), helpers_phy_ac.c (low-level
MHF/MACCTL helpers). Removes BROKEN from B43_PHY_AC Kconfig.

Signed-off-by: Alessio Ferri <alessio.ferri@mythread.it>
